00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:13,630
♪ Her graceful shadow sways ♪

220
00:10:14,490 --> 00:10:17,270
♪ New favors and old grudges
hard to dispel ♪

221
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:23,970
♪ How many things are now left behind? ♪

222
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:28,020
♪ Turning through time into a ballad ♪

223
00:10:28,880 --> 00:10:31,070
♪ I heard the legends rise like the wind ♪

224
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:33,070
♪ Only to fall back into nothingness ♪

225
00:10:33,850 --> 00:10:34,920
♪ I dare not disturb
the toll of the bell ♪

