00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:47,510
and you'll know.

235
00:10:46,910 --> 00:10:48,170
♪ Reincarnating in words ♪

236
00:10:49,090 --> 00:10:50,290
♪ Afraid others won't understand ♪

237
00:10:50,670 --> 00:10:53,290
♪ Afraid of stirring emotions
for no reason ♪

238
00:10:54,190 --> 00:10:59,570
♪ Better to have a beginning with no end ♪

